data.title: Capital City of Nepal]
data.meta_description: Capital city information to include weather, map, time, location and capital city name.
data.text: Capital - history name derives from the Kasthamandap temple that stood in Durbar Square; in Sanskrit, kastha means "wood" and mandapa means "pavilion"; the three-story structure was made entirely of wood, without iron nails or supports, and dated to the late 16th century; it collapsed during a 2015 earthquake
